If you have any problems using this skill, you can contact us at the following email address: contact@daewoo-security.fr

You can just ask Alexa to show you the camera.You don't have to go to your phone to view the camera - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
Connect Alexa to your Daewoo products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Daewoo Home Connect” application from the Android or iOS application market;
(2). Register a Daewoo account in our “Daewoo Home Connect” application;
(3). You must have some Daewoo devices on hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our“Daewoo Home Connect”application and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in the“Daewoo Home Connect”skills;
(5). Download the Amazon Alexa application from Android, iOS or Amazon App Market;
(6). Configure Echo with the Alexa application;
(7). Look for the skill “Daewoo Home Connect” in the skill category of the Alexa app;
(8). Click on Activate skill of “Daewoo Home Connect”, and you will be taken to the Daewoo login page;
(9). Enter the username and password for your Daewoo account, you will be redirected to the success page;
(10). Now your setup is complete.

You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, show me the camera
Alexa, turn on the socket
Alexa, turn off the socket
